high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the sink and stand in front of it facing it.
Pick up the butter knife that's to the left of the spoon.
Turn left and walk to the wall and turn left and walk to the counter.
Cut up the head of lettuce.
Put the knife on the counter by the yellow handled knife so it's hanging off the counter a little but so it will fall to the floor.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left and walk to the sink so you are standing in front of it facing it.
Wash the lettuce in the sink then pick it back up and turn off the water.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge and face it.
Put the slice of lettuce in the fridge on the shelf above the blue plate towards the front edge and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of a head of lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the metal knife to the left of the kitchen sink.
Turn left and walk to the wall, then turn left again and walk up to the section of kitchen counter to the right of the stove.
Use the knife to slice up the head of lettuce.
Place the knife on its point on the counter in front of the large metal knife with a golden handle.
Pick of a piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn left and begin walking across the kitchen, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Place the piece of sliced lettuce into the sink, turn the sink water on, wait a couple seconds then turn the water off and remove the piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the piece of sliced lettuce inside on the second rack from the bottom, then close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean piece of lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: turn left and walk forwards until you reach the sink on your right, then turn to face the sink and walk forwards towards it
grab the butter knife off of the left side of the kitchen sink
turn around and walk over to the right corner of the room
use the knife to cup up the lettuce on the counter there
set the butter knife down on the counter
pick up a lettuce slice off of the counter
turn around and walk forwards to the sink on the right
place the lettuce inside the sink, rinse it off, then pick it back up
turn to the right and walk to the fridge at the end of the room, then turn left to face the fridge
place the slice of lettuce inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed off slice of lettuce inside the fridge
